title: Warumbul, New South Wales
text:
Warumbul is a locality in the <a href="Royal%20National%20Park">Royal National Park</a> on the outskirts of <a href="Southern%20Sydney">southern</a> <a href="Sydney">Sydney</a>, in the state of <a href="New%20South%20Wales">New South Wales</a>, <a href="Australia">Australia</a>. Warumbul is located about 1.5 km southwest of <a href="Lilli%20Pilli%2C%20New%20South%20Wales">Lilli Pilli</a> on the southern side of <a href="Port%20Hacking">Port Hacking</a>.
Warumbul is the site of an Anglican Youth Department Conference Centre operated by <a href="Anglican%20Youthworks">Anglican Youthworks</a>.
